Chipmunks? Are you listening to the same copy as me?  I previously had the crazy-torrent cam copy and this one is much better.  The audio in particular is extremely better, the other copy had lots of static and  background chatter.  The video, although more washed out because it must have originally been pretty dark, is a straight even picture.  This is a great overall copy this early in the game.  I would say as compared to DVD, A-7 V-6.  Totally watchable.

I do want to point out that unless "Luna Nueva" is "New Moon" in Russian, which I do not speak, this is a Spanish copy, not Russian as listed.  The months of the year are all in Spanish too in the scene where Bella is in her room.
